                "content": "Christine Gymwear Co. was founded on the belief that activewear should empower, not limit. Our mission is to create performance-driven clothing that adapts to your lifestyle—whether you’re pushing limits in the gym or embracing spontaneity in your daily routine. We blend innovation with elegance to ensure every piece tells your story.",
